name: Magnetic Jewelry
description:
<html>
<head>
<title>Interactive Jewelry</title>
</head>

<body>
It's so fun and looks amazing! Each set is comprised of a ball chain and insanely strong ring magnet that can be fashioned into a necklace, bracelet, ring or anything else that strikes your fancy!  You can wear them separately or combine them to create different looks.  1 chain + 1 magnetic ring sold individually in a plastic tube. 
</body>

name: 3D Food Puzzles
description:
<html>
<head>
<title>3D Lunch Puzzle</title>
</head>

<body>
Excellent teaching tools for table etiquette, basic food groups, and nutrition. Food pieces can be used separately from the puzzle board for dramatic kitchen and grocery play. The name of each food is printed on labels in 5 different languages. Labels can be placed as needed to teach word/object recognition or promote foreign language development. PVC-free plastic pieces are safe for young tasters..... And The Most Important Part Of This Puzzle Is That It Is Super Fun!!!!!
</body>

</html>
